.. activecode:: bnm_fruitco_selection

    A fruit company sells oranges for 32 cents a pound plus $7.50 per order for shipping.  If an order is over 100 pounds shipping cost is reduced by $1.50.  Write a function that will take the number of pounds of oranges as a parameter and return the cost of the order.
